一名男子被老虎拖入虎園、咬至重傷。有目擊者稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">這名男子很可能是為要逃票，從後山爬入動物園</span>，誤闖虎園，最終虎咬。<br />\n<br />\n類似的事件曾在2006年發生，當地有4名年輕人，亦是為想逃票，於是翻過動物園後的小山、越過竹林、電網，進入動物園。可是，這些年輕人翻過多重障礙後，卻誤入非洲獅的地盤。<br />\n這四名年輕人較今日被咬的男子幸運，被飼養員發現，於是利用活雞引開獅子，並且召來獸醫、麻醉師前來，用麻醉槍、煙火連珠彈將獅子嚇走，將四人救出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeca057ed48084cfe969fb80ccc8037dc07c8462","tid":99691,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T12:00:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好擔心隻老虎 老虎無罪 希望佢無事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n死了"},{"pid":"68e89537958695ebabae7ef8b518f61f451620e6","tid":99691,"uid":46789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T12:09:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好擔心隻老虎 老虎無罪 希望佢無事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n死了</blockquote><br />\n老虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ec76ffbd15cca5c17384497e33d9e58dfe3130","tid":99691,"uid":41354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:02:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好擔心隻老虎 老虎無罪 希望佢無事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n死了</blockquote><br />\n老虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9285bb90570076341814d7d3895869376036634c","tid":99691,"uid":70399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:05:49.000Z","msg":"好慘呀 隻老虎"}]}